Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He only saw hell spread out\Nbefore his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes filled with regret and repent\Nare staring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can resist the fate\Nthat befell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When he controlled all,\Nhe thought he was immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, on that unforgettable day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the major catastrophe\Ndeprived people of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The chaos caused him\Nto become mortal once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As the gears grind into a new era...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,will their ignorance\Nbe proven?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,there are forty-eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As you suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the NMW seems to be\Nthe most vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obviously something\Nthey have not overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I advise you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.73,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what's called\N"statistical planning".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is indeed so, it proves\Nthat they still think like mortals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I want to ask you.\NDo you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are poor men\Nwho save themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,by praying to keep their\Nsole personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also imbeciles\Nwho learn nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,from killing thousands of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the one\Nto judge their values.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot promise\Nto be fair to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no turning back,\Nyou know that, Suzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not mind. My brother died,\Nand I accepted my fate to be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even plants die without water,\Nbut I lived on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to go, Master Ooga.\NDirect me to my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they were drugging people\Nwith words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Drugged people can do anything\Nand get off with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to stoop\Nto that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell us\Nwhat this Kaiser stone is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No lies. Tell us word for word\Nwithout twisting the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell you, but it may\Nbe difficult to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you should listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much knowledge will deprive you\Nof your beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My family's heritage is music.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My father and mother were both\Nwell-known composers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I inherited their skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With just one stroke\Nof an instrument...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,people around me applauded\Ntill their hands swelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My life was set\Nfrom the time I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered why we had the ability\Nto think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I met him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going by the name of Ooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gave me\Nthe Kaiser stone crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me that I can be reborn\Nwith it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that it was foolish\Nat the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was beautiful,\Nso I kept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the birth\Nof Hell-stinger, my counterpart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked it.\NThere were rumors of a dark night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep dreaming about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was immediately\Nawakened to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate reality,\Nbut at least it wakes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the death you've been\Nwaiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Say your prayers Ooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't satisfy me\Nwith that little toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is you.\NAll you want is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're trying\Nto do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't threaten me\Nwith such illusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the end.\NWe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you must do,\Neven if you have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My theory is that within him\Nis another him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean a double personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a doppelganger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're on the right track,\Nbut it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look who's talking?\N- Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why it's red?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't ask me.\N- The Kaiser stone is made from blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean it's made\Nfrom actual blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He is constantly fighting\Nwith this other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It may sound ridiculous,\Nbut it's stained with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Ooga's scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the leftover energy\Nthat flows out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from his will to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have no idea what you mean.\N- Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it in layman's terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's compare it to swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When a sword smith\Ncreates a masterpiece...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he always creates another sword\Nof the same shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the yin and the yang,\Nthe black and the white.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to create a sword\Nwith good powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he must create another sword\Nto absorb the evil powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the time of completion...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the evil sword\Nwill be condemned forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how a good sword is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser stone works the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As the negative energy within Ooga\Nexpands...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the positive energy\Nstarts to flow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, the good energy\Nhas the same amount of power as Ooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the positive power\Nof the Kaiser stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging to get what this little\NKaiser stone is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is this negative energy\Ntrying to destroy the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask\Nthe same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can laugh about it\Nall we want...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is definitely\Nsomething going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're blabbing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess we just\Nhave to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop Ooga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you were going to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably would have been\Nagainst it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I saw your Asahina-Twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to give you credit\Nfor your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be cynical.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I know the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not my style\Nto keep calm about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to lose, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our duty to save this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This planet's in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because the principal\Nis taken over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by some evil force, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my big chance\Nto save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed that you figured it out all\Nright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not talking about humans here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting against\Nan impenetrable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's crazy even for us who have the\Nability to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've got as a weapon\Nis that lousy stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's suicide\Nas far as I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that settles it. You just quietly\Nwait it out right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll invite you to the victory party\Nwhen it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanta go! I wanta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my parents always said I'd never\Nmeasure up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked all my life\Nto prove them wrong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I guess\Neveryone's got some kind of situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Set me right if I'm wrong about you\NOhga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Indian warriors fighting on foot\Nagainst the cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the long swim of an army of ants\Njoining together in a torrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could my life as\Ndetermined by will have any meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on over to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come'on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Area E West, Kanmon district, 100%\Ndeployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,120% penetration rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,150% control of sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No indeterminate factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Standby until further orders. Standby\Nlimit is 128 minutes. Over and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to work at the Gamon gate\Nno matter how hard we try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use the divine sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't use your ultimate weapon\Nat this early stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You will loose all of your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been measuring\Nhis strength all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the divine sword now\Nwill not adversely affect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are lying to me,\NMaster Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You think nothing of it even when your\Nflesh torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You rise up to fight even when your\Nbones are crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have witnessed\Nyour relentless spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please use my body\Nas much as you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let myself be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If he sees your spirit rising up from\Nyour body, that will be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be having trouble\Nwith that gate not opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry now that I, Misty Shaia,\Nhas arrived on the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt'll be as easy as pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hishizaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on. Why can't you play along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Misty Shaia,\Nthe mystery princess of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on. Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shaia, maybe we should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You are embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, even I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys shouldn't be so nosy about such\Nlittle details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you feel obliged\Nto lend me a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,after that talk we had this\Nafternoon, you're not welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely ran into you\Nat an outdoor concert. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss Shaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Triangle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate has opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her to a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch over my Master Kyosuke is the\Nmost important duty of my existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go along!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,On Kirikiara\NHaraharatsuta Yariaura Hila Hon Souka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open the door Master Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke! Master Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end? Is this the end of all\Nthat we've been through together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he sees your rising spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be given spellbinding power strong\Nenough to destroy with one glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer bear to see the face of\None who follows my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. So it is you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear friend,\Nyou're not acting like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You will never be happy with this silly\Ngame you are playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to have much patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well. Are we afraid? As the sands\Ncontinue to flow, slowly burying you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was a little more time, with\Nyou I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I will not say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The sands that fill up my ears must be\Ncleared away first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not only sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire and water\Nwill also support life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it plays a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as divine providence is not\Ndefied...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,life shall be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fake beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have spoken too much\Nabout what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a lot of things, without any\Nregard for your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... it's revenge, against your\Nbrother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,carried half of my burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness and despair, all of my\Nfeelings were for my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been seething within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think a person can live missing\Nhalf their body?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that I myself must\Ntake back, even if for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that half you are looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,can come from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want you to keep for\Nme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An earring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a keepsake from my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be going to where my sister is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wore something like this,\NI'd be laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you put it on for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I not learned anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I must never have those\Nthoughts again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you have awoken, Miss Shaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I saved you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,only because Master Kyosuke\Nordered me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you would have been left\Nabandoned in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,those were his final words and I could\Nnot ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,will not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like my warning\Nmeant nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of what you told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that I've been able to direct my powers\Nfor the purposes intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the timewhen all I thought\Nabout was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's quite a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any time to think\Nabout it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but you're\Ngetting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even feel his presence\Nwithin you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The perverted power...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hypocrisy of your devotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all very unsavory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be picking on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.77,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I have that right as his partner in\Ncrime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be under\Nhis spell as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave now. This is no place for low-rent\Nmercenaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you can always skip out on the\Nrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have to pay interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Having him confuse me\Nwith you two would be regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure likes to be dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll be fine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Retreat now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.72,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these\Ncreatures!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.15,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The most advanced weaponry\Nof the UN has no effect on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What is this young girl!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I will not loose against guys like\Nthese.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in a very good mood today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:24:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like some kind of theme park\NI went to as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.47,0:24:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Ohga built himself a nice little\Nplayground.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like the\NPrincess of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your day of reckoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.66,0:24:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you destroyed\Nmy other half...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.03,0:24:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a struggle even\Nto breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is where it\Nall ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.17,0:24:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.41,0:24:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what my brother\Ntold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.18,0:24:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you can fully utilize\Nthe Caizer stone's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on your psychological\Nstrength.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.52,0:24:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is when you have to protect\Nthe one you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.59,0:24:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are at your strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. My brother was\Nalways right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.56,0:25:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By accepting this\NCaizer stone into my body
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.50,0:25:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.37,0:25:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come to show you\Nthe power of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.70,0:25:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Metamol Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.93,0:25:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.53,0:25:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.51,0:25:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Isato Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Graviton...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.88,0:25:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraber!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Together they fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.32,0:26:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spirit of youthful camaraderie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.16,0:26:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato Kaiza...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.99,0:26:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In the spirit of his own jubilant\Nre-awakening...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.70,0:26:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he seeks to make amends for\Na wrong he committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.23,0:26:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He faces his vengeful foe, haunted like\Na criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.87,0:26:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash Mizutani...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped within the society he so\Ndespised...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.31,0:26:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and which he understood would soon meet\Nits own demise...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.28,0:26:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,he strives to unshackle himself from the\Nburdens of his childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.48,0:26:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke Shigure...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.12,0:26:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of revenge permeating his\Nbody.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.52,0:26:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting to prove his own worth as a\Nhuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,setting up the confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep within his conscience...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.26,0:26:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he was seeking to wipe out the memory\Nof his own brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.90,0:26:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a man who continues\Nto wait in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that he is waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a creation... or is it utter\Ndestruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.77,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.44,0:26:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The final chapter of this legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.64,0:27:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.61,0:27:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Voltage Fighter: Gowcaizer 3
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.82,0:27:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't learned a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.85,0:27:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again... neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.66,0:27:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.96,0:27:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.56,0:27:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.82,0:27:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.86,0:27:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.70,0:27:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.34,0:27:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get 'em, Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.51,0:28:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Cluster! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.44,0:28:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.11,0:28:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaen Henpou!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.08,0:28:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfection!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.74,0:28:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rub you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.71,0:28:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Gowcaizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.34,0:28:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Isato Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.60,0:29:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.37,0:29:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It is certainly not\Nmy intention to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.60,0:29:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.00,0:29:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've recently considered doing volunteer\Nwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.51,0:29:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I see that you're going to\Nvolunteer your life this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.98,0:29:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Graviton Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.22,0:29:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Beated Needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.07,0:29:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,On Bazaragini Harachihataya Souka.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.28,0:29:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.25,0:29:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not easy to be laying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:30:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been held in an unchanging state\Nover the past 3 years, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.33,0:30:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger will reduce your powers by half.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.97,0:30:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten\Nwhat I've taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.60,0:30:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.84,0:30:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one last question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.74,0:30:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.74,0:30:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to harm my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.71,0:30:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because you needed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it because you needed my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.98,0:30:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.22,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed Mia so that I could give you a\Nspecial power.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.29,0:30:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you were re-born\Nwith your new power...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.13,0:30:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to increase the strength\Nof that power...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.90,0:30:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mia had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.40,0:30:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my intention all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.54,0:30:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.31,0:30:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.17,0:30:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Day in and day out...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.18,0:30:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,late into dusk,\NI taught you how to use your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.55,0:30:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you responded very well in every\Nway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.18,0:30:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A most excellent ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.72,0:31:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.76,0:31:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything seemed to be proceeding just\Nas I wanted it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.86,0:31:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.73,0:31:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed that I miscalculated\Nsomething.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.63,0:31:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the love that you began to\Nshow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.93,0:31:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you saw me as a father figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.34,0:31:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.94,0:31:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to break\Nthat relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.98,0:31:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,although premature, I took the life of\NMia.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.88,0:31:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.11,0:31:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed that I'd made another\Nmiscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.18,0:31:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.22,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, the love she had for me was\Ndeeper than I could have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.56,0:31:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I sentenced her\Nto her death...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.16,0:31:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,she stepped forward\Nand offered her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.13,0:31:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.00,0:31:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,were the anguished cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.53,0:31:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke, it was the neck of Mia\Nas she cried for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.04,0:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It weighed heavily on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.07,0:31:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.91,0:31:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You were siblings hungering for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.04,0:32:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a question of disposition,\Nbut it's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.81,0:32:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.23,0:32:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush it, Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.30,0:32:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.10,0:32:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will reveal the other half\Nof my soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.20,0:32:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that of the providence of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.17,0:32:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.93,0:32:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.97,0:32:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.47,0:33:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to but in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.34,0:33:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay out of this, it'll end\Nquickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.98,0:33:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.31,0:33:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You want this to end in another\Nmeaningless sacrifice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.49,0:33:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you want then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.42,0:33:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But let me warn you first\Nthat she no longer has a human soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.46,0:33:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cheap humanistic approach will land\Nyou in a grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.90,0:33:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's the time to be\Nbickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.73,0:33:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you think I'm a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.07,0:33:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.94,0:33:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you merely plotting your response\Nto my attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.31,0:33:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.65,0:33:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Soul Gear! That's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.78,0:33:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.35,0:33:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you've got in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.29,0:33:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but you fool yourself if you think you\Ncan stand up to me without Soul Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzu Asahina!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.16,0:33:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If your goal is to kill me pure and\Nsimple...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.40,0:34:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm not going to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.11,0:34:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.19,0:34:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. You are human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.59,0:34:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you cause harm to another person...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.66,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you will surely be hurting\Nyour own soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.07,0:34:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However much you want to kill that\Nperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I will protect\Nyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Suzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.35,0:34:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.57,0:35:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.11,0:35:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.32,0:35:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash! Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.39,0:35:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, don't be\Ntaking advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.09,0:35:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like being called\Nonly when it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.19,0:35:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.10,0:35:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try to save her somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something weird going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.54,0:35:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.97,0:35:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of the Caizer is building up\Nwithin her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.58,0:35:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If it ruptures, that's the end of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.38,0:35:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop kidding around! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.35,0:36:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the authority on the Caizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.05,0:36:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.20,0:36:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.50,0:36:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my Caizer...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.84,0:36:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and align it against hers\Nto neutralize its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.37,0:36:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it fails, then I suppose we go to\Nheaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.98,0:36:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got other things\Nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.45,0:36:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.92,0:36:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.35,0:36:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.73,0:36:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He can run already.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.77,0:36:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure can recover quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.00,0:36:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just as you wished...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am volunteering to risk my life\Non account of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.97,0:37:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I develop such a\Nself-sacrificing character like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.11,0:37:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I was railing against all that\Nuptight society from my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.95,0:37:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Kash.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.29,0:37:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've been born into this\Nfamily...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.66,0:37:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you will lead a life in which your\Nperformances yield $10,000 per minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.93,0:37:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,10 minutes will yield you $100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.43,0:37:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore all distractions and never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.03,0:37:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone take your genius\Naway from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.00,0:37:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live your life for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.67,0:37:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Only for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.71,0:37:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.66,0:37:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Penetrate! Kamikabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.26,0:37:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.08,0:38:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body breaking apart already?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.65,0:38:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You mere human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.62,0:38:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When not in a group, you cannot stand up\Nalone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.92,0:38:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are foolish indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.19,0:38:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.06,0:38:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I am not the man you used\Nto know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At least on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.30,0:38:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am myself, and you,\Nand your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.04,0:38:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A great many people\Nare embodied within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.48,0:38:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.88,0:38:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.48,0:38:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.52,0:38:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it's beyond the understanding\Nof a dying man such as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.03,0:38:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you are the one\Nthey await.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.73,0:39:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Pygmalions worshipping the statue\Nthey created...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be but a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.74,0:39:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.11,0:39:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira! Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.61,0:39:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reprimand me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.02,0:39:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.80,0:39:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.88,0:39:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.33,0:40:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.57,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.21,0:40:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.94,0:40:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.25,0:40:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always considered this to be my\Nfinal duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.48,0:40:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In order for you to carry out\Nthat duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have had to return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.52,0:40:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am now all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.79,0:40:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.00,0:40:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.63,0:40:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always be near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.57,0:40:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.17,0:40:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.98,0:40:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.29,0:41:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.46,0:41:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.86,0:41:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiza?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.63,0:41:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.34,0:41:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.45,0:41:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be what Kash was talking\Nabout!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.06,0:41:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JG02. There is a mysterious\Nenergy emitting from...!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.23,0:41:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.74,0:41:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.64,0:41:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the will of all creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.14,0:41:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Omni Exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.28,0:42:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Omni Exist!?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.88,0:42:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The embodiment of all thought existing\Nin nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.15,0:42:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absorbed within me all of the\Ndesires of humankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.09,0:42:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I came into being.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.03,0:42:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.26,0:42:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have until now only existed as\Nthought.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.30,0:42:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shizuru Ozaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.87,0:42:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,His desires had reached the level\Nof my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.84,0:42:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And through him...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.85,0:42:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was first able to begin to carry out\Nmy destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.62,0:42:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You humans are despised...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.72,0:42:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,by all of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.86,0:42:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bound by the rules you created...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,an insane humanity bent on destroying\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.80,0:42:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The recklessness of disposing into outer\Nspace that which you cannot process...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.87,0:43:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who live on a planet bathed\Nin ultraviolet rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.61,0:43:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that reach every corner of the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.78,0:43:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.08,0:43:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction of earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.21,0:43:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the desire of all humankind, and I\Nam the one who will carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.65,0:43:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.22,0:43:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.43,0:43:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you've feared the future\Nat least at one time in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.83,0:43:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The good things and the bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.90,0:43:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It is surely frightening to look at the\Nfuture no matter what your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.31,0:43:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A world that does not progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.01,0:43:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is something that's certain to\Nbring relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.11,0:43:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the one you refer to as Kyosuke\Ndesires this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.02,0:43:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you wish it deep in your\Nsubconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.62,0:43:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.99,0:43:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.39,0:43:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.50,0:44:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But eventually, my powers will destroy\Nthe earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.60,0:44:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then all will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.51,0:44:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.14,0:44:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you will have to try and stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.58,0:44:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only succeed if either\Nyour energy exceeds mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.42,0:44:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or if all of existence can be\Npersuaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.02,0:44:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and cause me to completely loose\Nmy will.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.59,0:44:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Both seem preposterous at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.86,0:44:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.66,0:44:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm not much\Nof a pursuasive talker...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.86,0:44:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but to exceed your power is something\NI can give a shot at.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.84,0:44:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Caizer Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.12,0:44:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Caizer Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.10,0:45:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Burny Samona!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.65,0:45:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shaia.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.82,0:45:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Isato and them are gonna be all\Nright.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.45,0:45:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.59,0:45:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There're not going to loose that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.39,0:45:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.49,0:45:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not gonna loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.33,0:45:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.21,0:45:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit. I can't let it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.04,0:45:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Isato! It's not in your nature\Nto give up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.08,0:45:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.85,0:46:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.69,0:46:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.87,0:46:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.03,0:46:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing the kind of guy you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.97,0:46:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be playing up\Nthat high drama yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.74,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.44,0:46:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you do with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.58,0:46:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I delivered the princess to\Nher castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.62,0:46:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyper Voltage...!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.05,0:46:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform Hellstinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.42,0:46:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! And what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.53,0:46:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.03,0:46:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.96,0:46:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to round up the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.30,0:46:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, this might never\Ncome to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.24,0:46:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any of that at a time like\Nthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.07,0:46:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, to band together...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.54,0:46:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is a human tendency.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.78,0:47:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.88,0:47:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.12,0:47:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll set up a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.32,0:47:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You go straight for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.82,0:47:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.86,0:47:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lineck Singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.96,0:47:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.07,0:47:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.54,0:47:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.81,0:47:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my praise.\NI will now give you your reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.36,0:47:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sleepy, Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.93,0:47:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.33,0:47:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleepy, dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.30,0:47:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.04,0:48:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No Kyosuke. You mustn't sleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.34,0:48:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.01,0:48:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It is now that we need your strength the\Nmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.61,0:48:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kubira is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.22,0:48:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.22,0:48:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... I'm no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.86,0:48:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my hand, Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.53,0:48:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.36,0:48:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my final wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.20,0:48:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.54,0:48:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.51,0:48:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.68,0:48:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that the human will can be so\Nsublime...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.19,0:48:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.76,0:48:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We can be foolish and we often fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.19,0:48:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can also think evil thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.53,0:48:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.63,0:49:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,only humans will sacrifice their lives\Nto help save those close to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.34,0:49:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Well I'm just the kind of fool\Nthat'll fall for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.01,0:49:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your power to save everyone isn't\Nsomething that hasn't crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.65,0:49:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you what it's all about...!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.42,0:49:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The unlimited possibilities of human\Nbeings!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.55,0:49:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got quite an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.12,0:49:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is time that I show you the eternal\Nagony of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.19,0:49:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.19,0:49:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These forces are like no other we've\Nfelt yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.16,0:49:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.63,0:49:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish one...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.74,0:49:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.41,0:49:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.42,0:49:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.59,0:50:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you, my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.69,0:50:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.33,0:50:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.73,0:50:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time. Come Kaiza!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.97,0:50:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.70,0:50:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.67,0:50:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.54,0:50:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kash!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.21,0:50:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.22,0:50:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.09,0:50:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've paid my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.12,0:50:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.54,0:50:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here me well, humankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.08,0:50:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.92,0:51:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have not died.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.35,0:51:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a momentary lapse of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.63,0:51:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return at anytime that you\Ndesire.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.63,0:51:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.44,0:51:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isato...!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.28,0:52:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.42,0:52:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.03,0:52:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.66,0:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.40,0:53:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to bring you back.